PrecisAmendments to the CUSTOMS SUFFERANCE WAREHOUSES REGULATIONS which provide warehouse operators with certain procedural rights when their licence is suspended, abolish restrictions on the number of times that ownership of bonded goods may be transferred, allow for greater flexibility in determining minimum security deposits, and eliminate discrepancies between the English and French versions or make minor technical clarifications.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1995-0177 Publication Date: 1995-04-19
Attachments
precis:
Amendments to the CUSTOMS SUFFERANCE WAREHOUSES REGULATIONS which provide
warehouse operators with certain procedural rights when their licence is
suspended, abolish restrictions on the number of times that ownership of
bonded goods may be transferred, allow for greater flexibility in
determining minimum security deposits, and eliminate discrepancies between
the English and French versions or make minor technical clarifications.
